# ST0020/

Steel thread documenting the modernization of Intent's Elixir support from subagents-only to a layered skills + subagent architecture. Includes 11 work packages covering rule distillation, skill creation, infrastructure, testing, and project rollout across 7 implementation phases.

## Dirs

- `WP/` -- 11 work packages (WP-01 through WP-11) with individual info.md files for each phase

## Files

- `info.md` -- Steel thread metadata, objective, problem statement, solution architecture, work packages, and sequencing
- `design.md` -- Architecture decisions: skills vs subagents, three-file LLM guidance (AGENTS/RULES/ARCHITECTURE), Ash-first, rule consolidation, skill sizing
- `impl.md` -- Implementation phases (0-7), file inventory of new/modified files, and rollout status across 8 target projects
- `tasks.md` -- Complete task checklist organized by phase (0-7) covering documentation, foundation, skills, testing, infrastructure, upgrade, and rollout
